M||tx|---
M|Buil|tx|Multiple `.find()` calls by the same key shd use a Map.
M|Buil|**In|**
M|Buil|tx|```ts
M|Buil|func|Order[], us: us[]) {
M|Buil|tx|return orders.map(order => ({
M|Buil|tx|...order,
M|Buil|us|us.find(u => u.id === order.userId)
M|Buil|tx|}))
M|Buil|tx|}
M|Buil|tx|```
M|Buil|**Co|**
M|Buil|tx|```ts
M|Buil|func|Order[], us: us[]) {
M|Buil|tx|const userById = new Map(us.map(u => [u.id, u]))
M|Buil|tx|return orders.map(order => ({
M|Buil|tx|...order,
M|Buil|us|userById.get(order.userId)
M|Buil|tx|}))
M|Buil|tx|}
M|Buil|tx|```
M|Buil|tx|bd map once (O(n)), then all lookups are O(1).
M|Buil|For |1M ops → 2K ops.